channel.title: 194 cache, maps and deob HELP
channel.description:
What's up, a noob here. For a while now, I've been searching everywhere trying to find out how to get a 194 server to work. The problem a lot of people were having is that the 194 maps were missing, however, a short while back they were actually released by Scu11 himself. Right now, I have a 194 client and cache working together, all I need now is to find out how to get the maps working and what server to use to connect to it with. I have uploaded pictures of the cache, maps and deob and have also uploaded all the files. I really want to get this to work for nostalgic reasons, so it's highly appreciated. Thanks!
Download link: http://www.mediafire.com/?aba9gdvx6t67p8u
Maps [img]http://s21.postimg.org/ama26fwmv/Screen_Shot_2013_08_21_at_11_13_31.png[/img]
Cache + Deob [img]http://s23.postimg.org/4v2fcesyz/Screen_Shot_2013_08_21_at_11_12_51.png[/img]
Note: 194 is the earliest revision we have of RuneScape 2.
